Description_lang: Your harmful spells and abilities have a chance to conjure a cyclone at your current target's location. The cyclone follows the initial target dealing ${$s1* ($415339d/$s4)} Nature damage over $415339d split between all enemies.While inside the cyclone, enemies become Lightning Conduits. Dealing damage to a Lightning Conduit has a high chance to unleash a bolt of forked lighting, dealing $s2 Nature damage split between them and up to $s3 additional nearby targets.
